'''Mechanophilia''' is a [[a frank discussion of mental illness|mental disorder]] of the type [[paraphilia]]. It develops during the late [[Weev|anal period]] (5-7 years old). It is much more common among girls.

==Diagnostic criteria==
* Insertion of Barbie dolls/[[The_Virginmobile|model railway]]/[[Tamagotchi]] or similar into oneself's vagina/anus/peepeehole during early childhood.
* Have ever watched a [[animu#Chobits|Chobits]] episode.
* Hugging pillows.
* Intense, recurring, sexually arousing fantasies or dreams of [[dildo|anything without a heartbeat]] for a period of at least 6 months.
* Using a [[zeta toy]] - [[furry]] [[mecha]], extremely [[inconsistent personality disorder|fucked up]].
* Purchasing a [[dildo]]/artificial [[cunt|pussy]].
* Having an [[orgasm]] caused by a [[M._Chaos|butt machine.]]
* Sexual arousal by the thought of getting a pacemaker.
* [[Cyndilovespiccolo|Obsession with]] [[Transformers]] porn.
* [[You]] are [[Realmrsoptimusprime]]

==Prognosis==
Everything has been tried - even real, live intercourse with a [[prostitute]]. It didn't help. Possible reasons of this revealed by a scientific study conducted at [http://kyoto-u.ac.jp/ Kyodai] include:
* [[Fleshlight|Artificial pussies]]/[[anus|anuses]] are tighter than real human genitalia.
* [[Dildo]]s are more powerful/bigger than [[Quasidan's penis]].
* Hitachi Lick-o-matic with [[hookers and blow|Duracell batteries]] never wear out while real [[lesbian|carpet muncher]]s' tongues get tired pretty fast.
* Most importantly, real sex requires the participants to experience some ''emotions'', of which mecha are incapable.

The situation is not hopeless, however. [[Japan]]ese and [[Korea]]ns are already developing robots that have genitals mimicking that of humans, and mecha is lawful in most parts of the world.

